    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Workaround before this get merged:\r\n\r\n```\r\nimport Toggle from 'react-instantsearch/src/components/Toggle'\r\nimport { connectToggle } from 'react-instantsearch/connectors'\r\n\r\nconst FixedToggle = (props) => {\r\n  return (\r\n    <Toggle                                                                        \r\n      {...props}\r\n      currentRefinement={props.checked}\r\n    />\r\n  ) \r\n}\r\n\r\nconst ConnectedFixedToggle = connectToggle(FixedToggle)\r\n```\r\n\r\nThen use `ConnectedFixedToggle` instead of `Toggle`.",
