    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hi @klacointe, thank you very much for reporting this! \r\n\r\nI think the appropriate fix would be to rename the prop `checked` to `currentRefinement` inside the `connectToggle` connector. That way we stay consistent with all the other connectors. \r\n\r\nI can make the fix if you want, or you can modify your PR. Tell me what works best for you :)",
